- "I ate it!"

426
00:14:34,053 --> 00:14:36,593
- That makes your voice hoarse.
- "Chili sauce. Go for it!"

427
00:14:37,993 --> 00:14:39,433
I thought that was the end.

428
00:14:39,733 --> 00:14:41,193
But we went to another restaurant.

429
00:14:41,363 --> 00:14:44,233
