433
00:14:51,203 --> 00:14:54,013
- "It's cooked well! Go for it!"
- You were still Kwak Kyoung Young?

434
00:14:54,343 --> 00:14:55,573
When I said goodbye to him after the shoot,

435
00:14:56,713 --> 00:14:59,213
